lass="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：美国参议员迈克·李周四承诺，如果立法缺乏重大支出改革，将使用所有可用工具阻止任何可能提高债务上限的交易。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">来自犹他州的共和党人李说：“我将使用我掌握的所有程序工具来阻止不包含大量支出和预算改革的债务上限协议。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110584558" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/us-senator-vows-to-use-all-tools-to-impede-any-debt-ceiling-deal-without-spending-reform-1110584558.html?share-block=1110584559" data-title="“I will use every procedural tool at my disposal to impede a debt-ceiling deal that doesn’t contain substantial spending and budgetary reforms,” Lee, a Republican from Utah, said. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他对白宫和众议院议长凯文麦卡锡之间目前的谈判正朝着这个方向发展表示担忧。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “如果他们这样做，该提案将不会在参议院顺利通过，”他警告说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110584558" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230525/us-senator-vows-to-use-all-tools-to-impede-any-debt-ceiling-deal-without-spending-reform-1110584558.html?share-block=1110584562" data-title="“If they do, that proposal will not face smooth sailing in the Senate,” he warned. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周三，麦卡锡表示，国会共和党领导人和白宫在与提高美国 34.1 万亿美元债务上限相关的某些问题上仍存在很大分歧，这促使他派谈判代表进行另一轮谈判。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国众议院共和党人上个月通过了一项提高债务上限以换取削减政府开支的计划，尽管总统乔·拜登和参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默拒绝了该提议。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 25 May 2023 13:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/us-senator-vows-to-use-all-tools-to-impede-any-debt-ceiling-deal-without-spending-reform-1110584558.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230525/us-senator-vows-to-use-all-tools-to-impede-any-debt-ceiling-deal-without-spending-reform-1110584558.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category></item></channel></rss>